Support Staff Ratio

Tables

Histogram

0 are instances where the organization does not currently have vet hours, but they are currently looking to fill vet hours. 1 are instances where the organization does have vet hours, but they are not currently looking to fill any more vet hours. There are 183 instances where an organization does not have vet hours and is not currently looking to fill vet hours.

A high ratio generally means the current vet hours is substantially higher than the vet hours looking to fill. A low ratio generally means the opposite
